"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"10月26日，在万向区块链实验室主办的2021第七届区块链全球峰会上，以太链创始人维塔利克·布特林指出，扩展是区块链领域最大的挑战之一，实现区块链扩展有两种方法。就第 2 层技术而言，目前有两个主要分支的卷起技术，乐观卷起和 ZK 卷起，乐观卷起是短期内可行的选择，ZK 卷筒是长期首选。\",\"timestamp\":1636292688,\"title\":\"Vitalik Buterin: Scaling is one of the biggest challenges facing the blockchain space and Layer 2 is the future of Ethernet scaling\"},\"digest\":\"6PDfZSYmRrfsiyEo61f48gB-7ZTjyw7LJTUCB1dn3rQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd49D9fC2EEc9618F075fEC33e5f4E70dB68E70B8\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DrQ0DT3jMRV0rl20PDU5POByNoket8coED4nPMcdwLM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ui75SX-y831gghxA71fbhyFt6xUA3n24XJle5ORxs5g\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"dStXKot3OXmLFkkF6CJDZxUQOLoWIK347aG2J1pqMHfWsRWylQ_n-1ippFsOBKFPNPm5_UX3BjdNr6ERNSMFnQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0da7d676c0f2d4822642b2b61a171ec2008fce76ac13e473c8d49b2b3cd9c7421c7cffb85d6f0c2afacd7be833303282b3cca9344566714de4171656321a06411b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DrQ0DT3jMRV0rl20PDU5POByNoket8coED4nPMcdwLM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ui75SX-y831gghxA71fbhyFt6xUA3n24XJle5ORxs5g\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"6PDfZSYmRrfsiyEo61f48gB-7ZTjyw7LJTUCB1dn3rQ\"}"